# Format: Title | Description

# Password manager | Export recovery material not already covered by selected paths
# Mobile data | Confirm contacts, photos, and application exports are current
# GitHub secret values | Store Actions and webhook secret values separately; APIs expose names only
# Provider network state | Record VPS DNS, firewall, security-group, and rescue-console settings
# Offsite copy | Confirm one recent verified snapshot exists away from the primary backup disk
# Destination encryption | Confirm the sensitive-profile policy matches the mounted destination
# Offline recovery codes | Store them through an approved encrypted process
